title: The Imaginary Worlds of Winsor McCay (1911-1921) Silent Animation Compilation

sources.title: The Imaginary Worlds of Winsor McCay (1911-1921) Silent Animation Compilation
sources.description:
Winsor McCay (1869-1934)  was an influential American cartoonist and animator throughout the 20th century and beyond. This series of short silent films, don't just show the animated images or tell a story, but also showcase the entire animation process of the era.
